<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ràng quán shì jiè dōu tīng jiàn zhǔ shēng yīn, tiān guó jìn le dōu dāng xìn fú yīn.
 ràng yuē hàn zài kuàng yě yǒu lì de xuān jiǎng, jiǔ jiǔ huí dàng zài měi yī gè rén de xīn.
 tiān guó jìn le wǒ men dōu yào huǐ gǎi, xiàng zhe shén xiàng zhe shēn biān de měi yī gè rén.
 qiú zhǔ de bǎo xuè xǐ jìng wǒ men de xīn, chéng wèi shèng tǔ ràng zhǔ de ài zhā xià gēn.</lyrics>
<title>ràng quán shì jiè dōu tīng jiàn zhǔ shēng yīn 迦南1237</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1237</hymn_number>
</song>